<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Formulating Your BNB Tax Returns</h3>



<p>To properly report your Binance Coin (BNB) holdings for tax purposes, you must adhere to specific reporting requirements. Here are the steps you need to follow when formulating your BNB tax returns:</p>



<ol>
<li><strong>Calculate your BNB gains and losses: </strong>Determine the cost basis of your BNB holdings and calculate any gains or losses when you sell or trade them.</li>



<li><strong>Keep track of all transactions: </strong>Maintain detailed records of each BNB transaction, including the date, value, and purpose. This will help you accurately report your holdings and calculate your tax liabilities.</li>



